::Savanna/Spitfire::

Savanna::
"I hope so.  But what are they? Who are they working for?"
She transformed into bot mode and gets in.  She smiles and she slips 
into the seat. "Yeah, I was wondering when you were going to get me 
that drink."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Spitfire::

She walked a little closer and rested her hands on her hips.
She looked at the bounty hunters, hoping that she would at least get 
a few answers out of them.  She wrapped her long tail around her 
waist.  She tasted the air again. She could tell that these guys were 
not normally around ladies.
